B.HA=new A.hV("Magdou Health","Magdou Health app is a new innovative way to schedule on-demand radiology services for technologists. The app will be used by the health care facilities to order on-demand healthcare technologists to do their radiology exams. The technologist will be able to accept and complete the order from the app.","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.emam.magdouhealth","https://apps.apple.com/eg/app/magdou-health/id1627827916",null,"Developed at HarmoniQ Innovation Technology\nTrusted by tens of facilities and hundreds of technicians in the US",B.Dw,null,"2026","Live",B.Df)
